lead_paragraph: Three college football players from Michigan State University raised their fists during the U.S. national anthem on Saturday, emulating NFL players who have chosen the gesture to protest racial inequality.

headline.print_headline: Michigan State Football Players Emulate Raised-Fist Protest in NFL
